{"tid":1497410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[眾籌] 命運自選遙控器 抵制TVB","createTime":"2019-08-23T03:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T07:56:59.000Z","uid":291805,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4a344ebae03f2e7bb489c588d9e5491daa5bb2","tid":1497410,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2iknjJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2iknjJY.jpg&h=0a126482&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌網頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%91%bd%e9%81%8b%e8%87%aa%e9%81%b8%e9%81%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%99%a8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e5%2591%25bd%25e9%2581%258b%25e8%2587%25aa%25e9%2581%25b8%25e9%2581%2599%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2599%25a8%2F&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1UYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=7ac72bc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%91%bd%e9%81%8b%e8%87%aa%e9%81%b8%e9%81%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%99%a8/</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pi06MpD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPi06MpD.jpg&h=19159b7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTVB報導偏頗，不盡不實，屢次抹黑反送中示威活動，出賣香港市民。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在此呼籲全港18區抗爭者，合力將所有酒樓，茶餐廳，醫院，護老院，健身室等公共空間的電視轉台。<br />\n<br />\n由TVB 81/82/83/84/85 轉去 港台 31/32，開電視 77 或 Viu TV 99台。</span><br />\n<br />\n原post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320101/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320101/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟對萬用遙控略有認識，在過去一個月，與工廠開發了一款抗爭專用遙控器 (universal remote)。<br />\n<br />\n產品可控制<span style=\"color: red;\">9大電視品牌 + 1個自選品牌</span>，於出廠時已預設轉台及其他基本功能。 簡易操作如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 查看電視品牌<br />\n<br />\n2. 按鍵選擇該品牌<br />\n<br />\n3. 按CH+-鍵轉台<br />\n<br />\n現眾籌HKD120000，當中已包括開發和測試費用，4000件大貨，4%眾籌平台手續費，運輸到全港18區和18區智能櫃費用。</span><br />\n<br />\n如眾籌達標，將隨即下訂單，預計約30天內交貨。<br />\n<br />\n當貨到香港，將以捐款者提供的聯絡方式，告知所屬地區的取貨密碼和地址。<br />\n<br />\n這次眾籌屬個人自發，沒有人手，故只能用<span style=\"color: red;\">honour system</span>，煩請<span style=\"color: red;\">捐$50者自取一件，$100者自取兩件</span>，如此類推。 由於智能櫃有時間限制，請於通知發出後<span style=\"color: red;\">40小時內取貨</span>。 由於無法控制參與者是否全部自律，恕<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不能保證捐款者一定能取得產品，只能做到盡量安排，先到先得</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌目的，不像Kickstarter或Indiegogo買產品，而是<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要令更多的香港抗爭者加入全港轉台行列</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">多謝支持！！ 香港人加油！！</span>"},{"pid":"8ad77ddb62c269b42f1a3b0693e6b884e72d1b32","tid":1497410,"uid":24534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"e9214dc1e49110eaaa3e82c53b7fcd35b7895291","tid":1497410,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔起有冇人幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}